      {
        "subtopic": "Train Passing a Pole",
        "content": "**Q:** A train 180 m long runs at 54 km/hr. How much time will it take to pass a pole?\n**Solution:**\nSpeed = 54 × 5/18 = 15 m/s\nTime = 180 / 15 = 12 seconds\n**Answer:** 12 seconds"
      }
    ]
  },
