    "topic": "Practice Example 2",
    "subtopics": [
      {
        "subtopic": "Train Passing a Platform",
        "content": "**Q:** A 150 m long train crosses a platform 350 m long in 40 seconds. Find the speed.\n**Solution:**\nDistance = 150 + 350 = 500 m\nSpeed = 500 / 40 = 12.5 m/s = 12.5 × 18/5 = 45 km/hr\n**Answer:** 45 km/hr"
      }
